pattern generator:

- use NYT new-popular API, get the most popular articles
	
	- pull keywords from "all-views"

- store these keywords, url, timestamp into database

- loop through each keyword

	- send these keywords to twitter API (GetSearch)

	- check how many times that keyword has been tweeted/retweeted

- filter down the results


